<h1>Application Update</h1>

<p>Dear <%= @candidate.first_name %>,</p>

<p>
  Thank you for your interest in the <strong><%= @job.title %></strong> position at
  <strong><%= @organization.name %></strong> and for taking the time to apply.
</p>

<p>
  After careful consideration, we have decided to move forward with other candidates whose
  experience more closely aligns with the requirements for this particular role.
</p>

<p>
  This decision was not easy, as we received many qualified applications. We want you to know
  that we truly appreciate the time and effort you invested in your application.
</p>

<p>
  We encourage you to apply for future opportunities at <%= @organization.name %> that match
  your skills and experience. You can view our current openings at:
</p>

<p style="margin: 20px 0;">
  <%= link_to "View Open Positions", careers_url, style: "background-color: #0d6efd; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px;" %>
</p>

<p>
  Thank you again for considering <%= @organization.name %>, and we wish you the best in your
  job search and future career endeavors.
</p>

<p>
  Best regards,<br>
  The <%= @organization.name %> Recruiting Team
</p>
